&gt; profile:
&gt;
&gt; bin/heritrix --run conf/profiles/myprofile/order.xml
&gt;
&gt; But if heritrix is it already running, the job will never get started, 
&gt; and the only way I&#39;ve found to stop heritrix is via browser using the 
&gt; user interface.
